# ╭──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
# │                      Global Options                      │
# ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# ╭──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
# │                 Gmail Account                            │
# ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User gergely.wellner@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass show mbsync/gmail"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

